		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-14df96b4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="14df96b4" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-79d6d746 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode" data-id="79d6d746" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="shortcode.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div class="elementor-shortcode"><h3>Hours</h3><div class="ul_sl_hours"><h4>Audiology</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Friday: 8 a.m. to 4 p.m.</li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Crawford County Sports Medicine</h4>
<p><em>Please call for current hours</em></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>ENT (Ear, Nose, Throat)</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Thursday: 8 a.m. to 5 p.m.</li>
<li>Friday: 8 a.m. to 12 p.m.</li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Massage Therapy</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday &amp; Wednesday: 11:00 a.m. to 5:45 p.m.</li>
<li>Tuesday, Thursday, and Friday: 8:30 a.m. to 3:30 p.m.</li>
<li><em>Third Saturday</em> of the month: 8 a.m. to 12 p.m.</li>
<li>Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<h4></h4>
<h4>Meadville Workplace Health</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Friday: 7:30 a.m. to 4 p.m.</li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<h4></h4>
<h4>Orthopedic Associates of Meadville</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Friday: 7:30 a.m. to 4 p.m.</li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4></h4>
<h4>Outpatient Lab</h4>
<p><em>The final lab patient seen for the day must be registered 10 minutes prior to closing time.</em></p>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Friday: 6–11:30 a.m. and 12–2:30 p.m.<br />
<em>Closed for lunch 11:30 a.m. to 12 p.m.</em></li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Physical, Occupational, and Speech Therapy</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Thursday: 7 a.m. to 6:30 p.m.</li>
<li>Friday: 7 a.m. to 5 p.m.</li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Radiology</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday through Friday: 7 a.m. to 4 p.m.
<ul>
<li>All CT scan appointments must be scheduled — <strong>no walk-ins!</strong></li>
<li>For additional information about hours and scheduling exams visit our <a href="https://www.mmchs.org/services/radiology/">radiology page</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Vernon Women&#8217;s Center</h4>
<ul>
<li>Monday, Tuesday, Thursday, and Friday: 7 a.m. to 3:30 p.m.</li>
<li>Wednesday: 7:30 a.m. to 5 p.m.</li>
<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday: closed</li>
</ul>
</div></div>
						</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
